The paper discusses the use of machine learning on mobile devices, which falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of distributed computing, which falls under the category of "Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing" (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the use of mobile devices in a networked environment, which falls under the category of "Multiagent Systems" (cs.MA) and "Systems and Control" (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the privacy concerns associated with mobile devices, which falls under the category of "Networking and Internet Architecture" (cs.NI).
